{"tid":1408492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學野] 【小巴罷駛】青衣407小巴遭狂抄牌　返工時間堵路一度癱瘓長宏邨","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T18:31:49.000Z","uid":209679,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a3def59a76d3e602064fb801951d7b02346425","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"小巴407號線來往長宏邨及瑪嘉烈醫院。司機不滿近日屢遭票控，罷駛泊滿長宏邨巴士總站之餘，更將四部車擋住寮肚路轉彎往<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">青衣西路</span>處。罷駛維持約一小時，有青衣街坊表示事件導致寮肚路至青衣西路一帶交通嚴重擠塞，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">青衣西路不能左轉及右轉寮肚路。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿 青衣西路好緊要架<br />\n入機場<br />\n出大西北<br />\n又有幾個油站<br />\n又好多貨櫃車<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好阻到交勇阿！</span>"},{"pid":"d2eda31d0336fe71c78161983372af18384b644e","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243eb38d0870027bf76442ae9a7141f49fe076d2","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"交通！！<br />\nSorry 打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7deab8f82eeb426cdb9c170b60a5f128da1fd51","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MDtLS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MDtLS8.png&h=33ed894c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2514c98a6152af753b3cb5fdaa11a22c6784b953","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwWZSyq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwWZSyq.png&h=44a26af5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"134eaecab3e85aa81e06b3f216af92a26c5f1f68","tid":1408492,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0